otocol for an optimal outcome.\r\n\r\nDr. Jennifer Penrose has co-lectured with many local orthopedic surgeons and has gained valuable insight into their perspectives on surgical healing and recovery.  She will not hesitate to reach out to them if needed during your recovery process.\r\n\r\nTo the right, you will find a sample of surgical protocols that we typically use.  We will always communicate with your surgeon on your surgery and their preferred protocol.'),(556,70,'_content_builder_0_content','field_accordion_left_content'),(557,70,'content_builder_0_video_heading','Injury Rehabilitation Success Story'),(558,70,'_content_builder_0_video_heading','field_service_video_heading'),(559,70,'content_builder_0_video','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ppm5_AGtbTo'),(560,70,'_content_builder_0_video','field_service_video'),(561,70,'content_builder_0_video_image','19'),(562,70,'_content_builder_0_video_image','field_service_video_image'),(563,70,'content_builder_1_heading','Why choose us?'),(564,70,'_content_builder_1_heading','field_comparison_heading'),(565,70,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','Treatment'),(566,70,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','field_comparison_text'),(567,70,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_typical_text','Board certified in orthopedics (OCS)?  Do the therapists have experience co-lecturing  with local surgeons teaching the community about surgical rehabilitation?'),(568,70,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_typical_text','field_comparison_typical'),(569,70,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_comparison_text','Resources & Support'),(570,70,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_comparison_text','field_comparison_text'),(571,70,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_typical_text','Experienced in treating surgical rehabilitation and understanding the healing process and time frames of expected function?'),(572,70,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_typical_text','field_comparison_typical'),(573,