ment.  Supportive Atmosphere. Invaluable Advice.</h1>\r\nAn injury is painful, inconvenient, and costly in terms of time and finances.  We understand this is not where you want to be.  We want to help you move along this time line of healing as fast as possible.\r\n\r\nWith any injury it is vital to obtain the correct diagnosis.  At Penrose Physical Therapy we will provide a detailed orthopedic examination at the first appointment to determine what structures are involved and if you are appropriate for physical therapy or if a recommendation for another specialist is required.'),(612,74,'_content_builder_0_content','field_left_content'),(613,74,'content_builder_0_video_heading','Injury Rehabilitation Success Story'),(614,74,'_content_builder_0_video_heading','field_service_video_heading'),(615,74,'content_builder_0_video','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ppm5_AGtbTo'),(616,74,'_content_builder_0_video','field_service_video'),(617,74,'content_builder_0_video_image','233'),(618,74,'_content_builder_0_video_image','field_service_video_image'),(619,74,'content_builder_1_heading','Why choose us?'),(620,74,'_content_builder_1_heading','field_comparison_heading'),(621,74,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','Treatment'),(622,74,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','field_comparison_text'),(623,74,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_typical_text','Providing a thorough orthopedic examination and giving you a clear diagnosis?  Do you have quality hands on time with the therapist?'),(624,74,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_typical_text','field_comparison_typical'),(625,74,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_comparison_text','Resources & Support'),(626,74,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_comparison_text','field_comparison_text'),(627,74,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_typical_text','Teaching you how to tape yourself?  Do they provide practical and immediate methods to self treat?'),(628,74,'_content_builder_1_comparison