</h2>\r\nOsteoporosis is a silent disease that weakens your bones.  1 in 2 women and 1 in 4 men age 50 and older will break a bone due to osteoporosis. If you have been diagnosed with osteoporosis, come to Penrose PT to learn how to move without risking a fracture. We will teach you how to increase bone density with progressive weight lifting, impact exercise, and safe resistance exercise.\r\n\r\nOur program will include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>posture</li>\r\n 	<li>core strength</li>\r\n 	<li>correct squatting and lifting</li>\r\n 	<li>balance training</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe welcome your questions and will keep your osteoporosis in mind to progress you safely.'),(706,76,'_content_builder_0_content','field_left_content'),(707,76,'content_builder_0_video_heading','Injury Rehabilitation Success Story'),(708,76,'_content_builder_0_video_heading','field_service_video_heading'),(709,76,'content_builder_0_video','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ppm5_AGtbTo'),(710,76,'_content_builder_0_video','field_service_video'),(711,76,'content_builder_0_video_image','19'),(712,76,'_content_builder_0_video_image','field_service_video_image'),(713,76,'content_builder_1_heading','Why choose us?'),(714,76,'_content_builder_1_heading','field_comparison_heading'),(715,76,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','Treatment'),(716,76,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','field_comparison_text'),(717,76,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_typical_text','Measuring your height and calculating your historical height loss to see if you may have a silent verterbral compression fracture?'),(718,76,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_typical_text','field_comparison_typical'),(719,76,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_comparison_text','Resources & Support'),(720,76,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_comparison_text','field_comparison_text'),(721,76,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_1_typical_text','Giving you clear guidelines on  how much weight to lift and which