'Skilled Treatment.  Supportive Atmosphere. Invaluable Advice.'),(751,77,'_content_builder_0_heading','field_service_heading'),(752,77,'content_builder_0_content','<h2>Skilled Treatment.  Supportive Atmosphere. Invaluable Advice.</h2>\r\nJennifer Penrose, DPT, OCS, MTC and Kristen Weaver, MSPT, Cert MDT, CMPT are both certified manual therapists.  Manual therapy involved specialized techniques where the therapist uses their hands to manipulate joints and soft tissue structures. In addition, they increase mobility and decrease pain.  Contract relax, manual stretching, mobilization with movement, and strain-counterstrain are all hands on techniques we use.\r\n\r\nManual therapy can also help decrease swelling with a special massage technique.  Chris Edwards, PTA our assistant also has training in manual techniques to assist in your recovery.\r\n\r\nDr. Penrose and her assistant Chris Edwards are <strong>Graston Trained</strong> and will use both metal and plastic instruments for soft tissue mobilization in addition to their hands.  We can even teach you how to use the plastic instruments should you want to purchase your own for home use.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(753,77,'_content_builder_0_content','field_left_content'),(754,77,'content_builder_0_video_heading','Injury Rehabilitation Success Story'),(755,77,'_content_builder_0_video_heading','field_service_video_heading'),(756,77,'content_builder_0_video','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ppm5_AGtbTo'),(757,77,'_content_builder_0_video','field_service_video'),(758,77,'content_builder_0_video_image','19'),(759,77,'_content_builder_0_video_image','field_service_video_image'),(760,77,'content_builder_1_heading','Why choose us?'),(761,77,'_content_builder_1_heading','field_comparison_heading'),(762,77,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','Treatment'),(763,77,'_content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_comparison_text','field_comparison_text'),(764,77,'content_builder_1_comparison_table_0_typical_text','Ma