 Capital Forest Mountain marathon.  These are not for the faint of heart.  If you are looking for a challenge to run steep trails this is the race for you!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-298 size-medium\" src=\"https://penrosept.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sponsorGR1-225x300.jpeg\" alt=\"guerilla womens cross country\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />','Guerilla Running Sponsor','Penrose Physical Therapy proudly sponsors Guerilla running club.   ','publish','open','open','','guerilla-running-sponsor','','','2017-02-10 20:22:32','2017-02-10 20:22:32','',0,'http://penrose1.wpengine.com/?p=349',0,'post','',0),(352,1,'2017-01-19 21:22:54','2017-01-19 21:22:54','','a3kQXBw','','inherit','open','closed','','a3kqxbw','','','2017-01-19 21:22:54','2017-01-19 21:22:54','',0,'http://penrose1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/a3kQXBw.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(355,3,'2017-01-20 01:32:54','2017-01-20 01:32:54','','marrisafun','','inherit','open','closed','','marrisafun','','','2017-01-20 04:26:04','2017-01-20 04:26:04','',16,'http://penrose1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/marrisafun.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(358,3,'2017-01-20 01:41:26','2017-01-20 01:41:26','','marissahead','','inherit','open','closed','','marissahead','','','2017-01-20 01:41:30','2017-01-20 01:41:30','',16,'http://penrose1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/marissahead.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(359,3,'2017-01-20 04:18:20','2017-01-20 04:18:20','','trinahead','','inherit','open','closed','','trinahead','','','2017-01-20 04:18:24','2017-01-20 04:18:24','',16,'http://penrose1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/trinahead.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(360,3,'2017-01-20 04:18:46','2017-01-20 04:18:46','','trinafun','','inherit','open','closed','','trinafun','','','2017-01-20 04:18:50','2017-01-20 04:18:50','',16,'http://penrose1.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/trinafun.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(362,3,'2017-01-20 05:11:07','20