ger with a reputable online marketing company based in India.\r\n\r\nWe can fairly quickly promote your website to the top of the search rankings with no long term contracts!\r\n\r\nWe can place your website on top of the Natural Listings on Google, Yahoo and MSN. Our Search Engine Optimization team delivers more top rankings than anyone else and we can prove it. We do not use \"link farms\" or \"black hat\" methods that Google and the other search engines frown upon and can use to de-list or ban your site. The techniques are proprietary, involving some valuable closely held trade secrets. Our prices are less than half of what other companies charge.\r\n\r\nWe would be happy to send you a proposal using the top search phrases for your area of expertise. Please contact me at your convenience so we can start saving you some money.\r\n\r\nIn order for us to respond to your request for information, please include your company’s website address (mandatory) and or phone number.\r\n\r\nSo let me know if you would like me to mail you more details or schedule a call. We\'ll be pleased to serve you.\r\nI look forward to your mail.\r\n\r\nThanks and Regards\r\nMax Alias Jitesh'),(84,12,3,1.3,'Ashley'),(85,12,3,1.6,'Carter'),(86,12,3,2,'(904) 770-3502'),(87,12,3,3,'acarter@usa.edu'),(88,12,3,4,'Student Affiliation Agreement Renewal'),(89,12,3,6,'Good afternoon Ms. Penrose,\r\n \r\nMy name is Ashley Carter and I am the contracts administrator at the university. \r\nOur student affiliation agreement is set to expire on July 4, 2017 and I would like to start the renewal process at this time, if possible. \r\nIs there someone I need to contact first to get approval?\r\nThank you and I look forward to hearing back from you. \r\n\r\nAshley Carter, BA\r\nContracts Administrator\r\nUniversity of St. Augustine for Health Sciences\r\nPhone: 904-770-3502\r\n1 University Boulevard | St. Augustine, FL  32086\r\n(904) 770-3502  | fax (904) 339-9285 \r\nwww.usa.edu  |  acarter@usa.edu'),(90,13,3,1.3,'Paul'),(91,13,3,1.6,'Solberg'),(92,13,3,2,'(360) 789-0490'),(93,13,3,3,'Paulvsolberg@yahoo.com'),(94,13,3,4,'Grapevine'),(95,13,3,6,'Please send me the DR\'s name so I can setup the constitution.\r\n\r\nThank you\r\n\r\nPaul?'),(96,14,1,1.3,'Tony Nyers'),(97,14,1,2,'(574) 876-9608'),(98,14,1,3,'tnyers@healygroup.com'),(99,14,1,4,'Worked with you recently'),(100,14,1,6,'Popped my left calf Friday running on the beach.  Let me know when you can get me in to look at it.'),(101,14,1,7.1,'Sign me up for Penrose newsletter'),(102,15,1,1.3,'Sonya Hamberg'),(103,15,1,2,'(206) 851-9822'),(104,15,1,3,'sonya.hamberg@gmail.com'),(105,15,1,4,'Dr femiano - Oly Ortho referral'),(106,15,1,6,'I need help with a bulging disk in my C5/6 region - traction to help alleviate the pain in conjunction with treatment at Oly Ortho. I can see you this afternoon (14th) after 2.30, tomorrow (15th) morning, or Friday after 4. I would love to get in as soon as possible to begin my recovery. \r\n\r\nNext week I could do Monday or Tuesday afternoon. \r\n\r\nThank you for your time! Best. \r\n-Sonya'),(107,16,3,1.3,'Mark'),(108,16,3,1.6,'Merklin'),(109,16,3,2,'(360) 491-8195'),(110,16,3,3,'mmerklin@minutemanpress.com'),(111,16,3,4,'I visited your office'),(112,16,3,6,'When I was there someone was saying that your office may be interested in ordering custom T shirts. I have just recently added a link to our website that will allow you to search literally millions of promotional items including apparel. Please visit our website and click on the link that says \"Search for Promotional Items.\"\r\n\r\nHave fun. Let me know if you see anything you may be interested in.'),(113,17,3,1.3,'Mark'),(114,17,3,1.6,'Merklin'),(115,17,3,2,'(360) 491-8195'),(116,17,3,3,'mmerklin@minutemanpress.com'),(117,17,3,4,'Office visit'),(118,17,3,6,'When I was there someone was saying that your office may be interested in ordering custom T shirts. I have just recently added a link to our website that will allow you to search literally millions of promotional items including apparel. Please visit our website and click on the link that says \"Search for Promotional Items.\"\r\n\r\nwww.Lacey-Wa.minutemanPress.com\r\n\r\nHave fun. Let me know if you see anything you may be interested in.'),(119,18,1,1.3,'Pameula'),(120,18,1,2,'(360) 427-0932'),(121,18,1,3,'kamsgrannie@yahoo.com'),(122,18,1,4,'Dr. Singha'),(123,18,1,6,'I have been doing SI injections, I have severe SI joint problems. Dr. Singha recommended I see you. I did have physical therapy for about 9 months last year for this.'),(124,18,1,7.1,'Sign me up for Penrose newsletter'),(125,19,3,1.3,'Pameula'),(126,19,3,1.6,'Sloan'),(127,19,3,2,'(360) 427-0932'),(128,19,3,3,'kamsgrannie@yahoo.com'),(129,19,3,4,'hospital'),(130,19,3,6,'Please cancel my appt scheduled on may 1st. Thank you'),(131,20,3,1.3,'JoAnn'),(132,20,3,1.6,'Sadler'),(133,20,3,2,'(855) 369-3923'),(134,20,3,3,'jsadler@medincrease.com'),(135,20,3,4,'Google'),(136,20,3,6,'By way of introduction my name is JoAnn Sadler and I am with MediNcrease Health Plans, a national provider network.  \r\n\r\nWe are working with clients and payers that are looking to maintain access for existing business and gain new access to services through our network.  Approximately 400 payers (health insurers, insurance companies, employer groups, benefit plan administrators, and other companies involved in the management of medical claims) representing more than 5.5 M covered lives now have access to our national provider network.\r\n\r\nI would certainly appreciate it if you could direct me to the managed care contractor.  Thank you for your time and I look forward to hearing back.\r\nKindly,\r\n\r\nJoAnn Sadler\r\nVice President, Network Development\r\n \r\n5999 Central Avenue, Suite 401\r\nSt. Petersburg, FL 33710\r\n(855) 369-3923 Toll Free, Ext. 410\r\n(866) 654-4993 Fax\r\njsadler@medincrease.com\r\nVisit our website: www.medincrease.com'),(137,21,3,1.3,'Jason'),(138,21,3,1.6,'Asperin')