hen compared to whey protein isolate, it delivers 3 x greater anabolic response and 3 x greater net gain of muscle protein.  I would love to share more info, if you are interested.\r\n\r\nAll my best,\r\n\r\nRuss'),(166,26,1,1.3,'Toni Swift'),(167,26,1,2,'(360) 878-0919'),(168,26,1,3,'tswift.d1@gmail.com'),(169,26,1,4,'online search'),(170,26,1,6,'Referral for physical therapy from Dr. Maria Christina Dajoyag Mapili (253-792-6526, MultiCare Lakewood Family Practice).  \r\n\r\nPatient is Toni Swift, contact number noted above. \r\nFist Choice Health, MultiCare Health System\r\nID#870066417-01, Group#5200\r\nOpen Referral. Auto Authorization: 202106639-MHS ADT Auth/Ref tracking\r\nStart date 4/10/17 through 12/31/2017, valid for 8 visits.\r\nDiagnosis: 724.2, 724.3, 338.29 (ICD-9-CM) - M54.41, M54.42, G89.29 (ICD-10-CM) - Chronic midline low back pain with bilateral sciatica.\r\n\r\nI\'m requesting an appointment for Tuesday June 13 after 2 PM if possible. Next available appointment at early morning or late afternoon after June 13th.  \r\n\r\nThank you.');
